body: Keep to yourself and do only your job. There is no organization you will be required to do your job and everyone else’s. Favoritism is a thing here. If you like a job where you can sit around complain not be held accountable for anything you do then this is the place for you. There is no training no communication although they stress it. Place is a outright joke and doesn’t care about their employees whatsoever. They monitor your every move with the cameras mounted over your shoulder.
